Urbain Cancelier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Urbain_Cancelier 0 Urbain Cancelier (born 2 August 1959) is a French comedian and actor, primarily known for his collaborations with French film director Jean-Pierre Jeunet, and for playing Collignon in Le Fabuleux Destin d'Amélie Poulain.
